translation[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,1,Yeh hai woh surat jo hum ney nazil farmaee hai aur muqarrar ker di hai aur jiss mein hum ney khulli aayaten (ehkaam) utaray hain takay tum yaad rakho
  24,2,Zina kaar aurat-o-mard mein say her aik ko so koray lagao. Inn per Allah ki shareeat ki hadd jari kertay huye tumhen hergiz tars na khana chahaye agar tumhen Allah per aur qayamat kay din per eman ho. Inn ki saza kay waqt musalmano ki aik jamatmojood honi chahaye
  24,3,Zaani mard ba-juz zaaniya ya mushrika aurat kay aur say nikah nahi kerta aur zina kaar aurat bhi bajuz zaani ya mushrik mard kay aur nikah nahi kerti aur eman walon per yeh haram ker diya gaya
  24,4,Jo log pak daman aurton per zina ki tohmat lagayen phir char gawah na paish ker saken to unhen assi koray lagao aur kabhi bhi unn ki gawahee qabool na kero. Yeh fasiq log hain
  24,5,Haan jo log iss kay baad toba aur islah ker len to Allah Taalaa bakshney wala aur meharbani kerney wala hai
  24,6,Jo log apni biwiyon per bad-kaari ki tohmat lagayen aur unn ka koi gawah ba-juz khud unn ki zaat kay na ho to aisay logon mein say her aik ka saboot yeh hai kay char martaba Allah ki qasam kha ker kahen kay woh sachon mein say hain
  24,7,Aur paanchwen martaba kahey kay uss per Allah ki lanat ho agar woh jhooton mein say ho
  24,8,Aur uss aurat say saza iss tarah door hosakti hai kay woh char martaba Allah ki qasam kha ker kahey kay yaqeenan iss ka mard jhoot bolney walon mein say hai
  24,9,Aur paanchwen dafa kahey kay uss per Allah Taalaa ka azab ho agar uss ka khawind sachon mein say ho
  24,10,Agar Allah Taalaa ka fazal-o-karam tum per na hota (to tum per mushaqqat utarti) aur Allah Taalaa toba qabool kerney wala ba-hikmat hai